import React from "react";
import Button from "@material-ui/core/Button";
import TextField from "@material-ui/core/TextField";

export const Form = (props) => {
  return (
   <form onSubmit={() => {}}>
     <TextField
       id="name"
       name="name"
       label="Name"
       fullWidth

     />
     <TextField
       id="email"
       name="email"
       label="Email"
       fullWidth
     />
     <TextField
       id="password"
       name="password"
       label="Password"
       fullWidth
       type="password"
     />
     <TextField
       id="confirmPassword"
       name="confirmPassword"
       label="Confirm Password"
       fullWidth
       type="password"
     />
     <Button
       type="submit"
       fullWidth
       variant="raised"
       color="primary"
     >
       Submit
     </Button>
   </form>
 );
};
